701\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1912701</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n佢地都真係好有心 希望大家可以支持下佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>特別係hgds1266個ig <br />\nfollower一直得好少咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n多謝大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n求CLS+推po<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc4fb95952c1eb6ddc3f5548c88d944c5032e907","tid":1913611,"uid":54653,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T02:55:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2oB94zU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2oB94zU.jpg&h=a0a9f1f7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8a69b099533566a2a15fc5a0f032345400b32aed","tid":1913611,"uid":34777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T02:56:11.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid